<%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <h1>
            <%= title %>
        </h1>

        <p>Discover service projects designed to make a positive impact in communities around the region. These projects
            connect volunteers with meaningful work across a range of focus areas.</p>

        <section>
            <h2>Featured Service Projects</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Park Cleanup Initiative</strong> — Help restore local green spaces by removing litter,
                    planting native flowers, and improving public trails.</li>
                <li><strong>After-School Tutoring</strong> — Support students with homework help, reading practice, and
                    mentorship in a safe learning environment.</li>
                <li><strong>Neighborhood Food Drive</strong> — Organize donations, pack care kits, and deliver food to
                    families in need.</li>
                <li><strong>Health Awareness Fair</strong> — Assist community partners with wellness booths, screenings,
                    and health education outreach.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>How to Get Involved</h2>
            <p>Browse projects by category, choose one that matches your interests, and join other volunteers to make a
                real difference. Every project helps build stronger communities.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>